profile:
Gary Wenzel, President of Gary Wenzel Electrical and Fire Alarm Solutions, is a Master Electrician, as well as a CFAA Certified Fire Alarm Technician. With many years experience in residential, commercial and industrial installations, inspections, sales and servicing of electrical and fire alarm equipment.


Master Electrician
CFAA Certified Fire Alarm Technicians
Licensed ESA Electrical Contractor
CFQ Construction Electricians
Full Insured, 24 Hour Service
Bucket Truck Services

We are following all the health and safety protocals to ensure everyone is safe while we are on site.
